{"tid":2000710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈效應真係勁，好感動","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T05:53:01.000Z","uid":160555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b85162f029e0bc38c23da956496bff420be5f8e","tid":2000710,"uid":160555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"好撚多藍屍，共狗都腳震。又話黃色經濟圈冇用嘅？<br />\n<br />\n而家先黎出口術都冇用啦，排隊等執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a782ac05cdd9ea3b9c652a6d6b17bbc84efbe58","tid":2000710,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"仲要多謝武肺助功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9f7c00e50e4c3c55bc798aaf0a9f40d8b0eb49","tid":2000710,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a29140efd2f3e76b98657b2ed8c11ef72094cf5","tid":2000710,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}